  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Captain Darnath Lysander leads the Imperial Fists' First Company to the world of Opis, where the planetary defence force has fractured into civil war and the Imperium's grip is slipping. The Seventh Crusade-company response is meant to be a clean intervention, but the rebellion proves to be a front for a Chaos cult deep inside the Opisian aristocracy — and the cult's master reaches back into Lysander's own captivity under Warsmith Shon'tu of the Iron Warriors. Officio Assassinorum operatives stiffen the late push. A grim Imperial Fists chapter-piece on the cost of uncompromising siegecraft.",
